{"id":232234346,"title":"10/26動保講座【生命教育，從動物保護談起】","content":"[天河教育基金會 x TSPCA 公益講座] \n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/gYNS8P4.jpg\n\n 本次的公益講座──【生命教育，從動物保護談起】，\n精選三位講者帶領大家從校園動物出發，\n以動物保護議題為主軸，\n透過經驗分享、觀念交流的過程，\n反思動物教我們的生命課題。\n\n講座時間：10/26(六) 10:00-15:30（9:50開始報到）\n講座地點：Homeholic共享空間（台北市中正區漢口街一段82號2樓）\n講者：\n1. 香蕉(王俊傑)/ 藝人、外景節目主持人\n2. 紀俊麟/ 台大醫師、沐懷管理顧問公司執行長\n3. 許哲瑋/ 台灣防止虐待動物協會(TSPCA) 教育推廣專員\n\n公益講座免費入場，快揪團報名吧！\n\n以下報名連結內有更詳細的講者及講題介紹，\n歡迎將講座資訊分享給更多關注動物議題的親朋好友唷～\n>>> 報名網址：https://reurl.cc/Rd198e","excerpt":"［天河教育基金會 x TSPCA 公益講座］，本次的公益講座──【生命教育，從動物保護談起】，精選三位講者帶領大家從校園動物出發，以動物保護議題為主軸，透過經驗分享、觀念交流的過程，反思動物教我們的生","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"2bb20844-07ec-41d3-830f-ae551fc31246","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-05T03:23:53.030Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-05T03:23:53.030Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["動物保護","動物平權","校園動物","公益講座"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"課程","forumAlias":"course","school":"國立臺灣科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/gYNS8P4.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"2d59e837-f8a8-420a-8451-67e1385393d0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/gYNS8P4l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/gYNS8P4l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/gYNS8P4l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-05T03:23:53.030Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-05T03:23:53.030Z"},{"id":"2d59e837-f8a8-420a-8451-67e1385393d0","url":"http://i.imgur.com/gYNS8P4.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/gYNS8P4","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/gYNS8P4l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-05T03:23:53.030Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-05T03:23:53.030Z"}]